stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Initialized: App loads

    Initialized --> HomePage: htmx loads home.html
    HomePage --> HomePage: Click nav Home
    HomePage --> AlgoPage: Click algorithm card

    AlgoPage --> LoadingSetup: setupCurrentAlgo()
    LoadingSetup --> AlgoReady: setup() succeeds
    LoadingSetup --> SetupError: setup() throws
    SetupError --> AlgoReady: User retries

    AlgoReady --> ReadyToRun: User clicked algo
    ReadyToRun --> Running: Click Run
    ReadyToRun --> Stepping: Click Step
    ReadyToRun --> Resetting: Click Reset

    Running --> Running: Interval tick
    Running --> Paused: Click Pause
    Running --> Complete: All steps done
    Running --> Resetting: Click Reset

    Stepping --> ReadyToRun: Step complete
    Complete --> ReadyToRun: Reset
    Resetting --> Initialized: Clear state
    Resetting --> ReadyToRun: Re-render sidebar